metadata.name: Hazard Freak 862
metadata.description:
Unique, Radiation-ridden Hazard Freaks wondering around the contaminated Metaverse | Fully 1 of 1 NFT Collection.

Hazard Freaks are about art! We promise you an association with your freak. A unique connection and a world where you and your freak become one. We wanted to illustrate the true nature of every person. The freakishness that's within each one of us, and the uniqueness that's connected to our unique personalities!
